import React from 'react'
import {FooterContainer, FooterSubscription, FooterSubheading, FooterSubText} from './Footer.elements'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <FooterContainer>
            <FooterSubscription>
                <FooterSubheading>
                    Shoot us some Feedback!
                </FooterSubheading>
                <FooterSubText>
                    We'll read every comment. Promise.
                </FooterSubText>
            </FooterSubscription>
        </FooterContainer>
    ) 
}

export default Footer
